@startuml WebSocket Chat

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam participantPadding 12
skinparam boxPadding 8

actor "User A" as A
actor "User B" as B
participant "Frontend A" as FA
participant "Frontend B" as FB
participant "Handler" as H
participant "Service" as S
participant "Hub" as Hub
participant "imageproc" as IP
participant "DB" as DB
participant "S3" as S3

== Open / find conversation ==

A -> FA: open chat with B
FA -> H: POST /chat/conversations {peer_user_id}
H -> S: OpenConversation(A, B)
S -> DB: UPSERT conversations\n(normalize: userA < userB)\nON CONFLICT DO NOTHING
DB --> S: conversation
S --> H: conversation
H -> DB: GetConversation + UnreadCounts\n+ LastMessageBodies (DISTINCT ON)
DB --> H: ConversationView
H --> FA: 200 {id, peer_name, unread_count}

== User B connects via WebSocket ==

B -> FB: open chat
FB -> H: GET /conversations/{id}/ws?token=<jwt>
note right: Browser can't send\nAuthorization header\nfor WebSocket upgrades
H -> H: ValidateToken → userID=B\nEnsureParticipant(convID, B)
H -> Hub: Register(B, conn)
Hub -> Hub: users[B][client] = {}\ngo writePump(client)
H --> FB: 101 Switching Protocols

== Send text message ==

A -> FA: type message
FA -> H: POST /conversations/{id}/messages\nmultipart body="Hello"
H -> S: SendMessage(convID, sender=A, body)
S -> DB: BEGIN\nINSERT chat_messages RETURNING id, created_at\nUPDATE conversations SET last_message_at=NOW()\nCOMMIT
S -> Hub: SendToUser(B, {is_mine:false, body})
Hub --> FB: wsjson.Write → 🔔 new message
S -> Hub: SendToUser(A, {is_mine:true, body})
Hub --> FA: echo to other tabs
H --> FA: 201 {id, body, created_at}

== Send photo (any format → WebP) ==

A -> FA: attach photo (JPEG/PNG/HEIC/…)
FA -> H: POST /conversations/{id}/messages\nmultipart file=photo
H -> H: DetectMIME(magic bytes)\nIsSupported?
H -> IP: Convert(src)
IP -> IP: guardPixels (DecodeConfig ≤40MP)\ndecode → resize ≤2048px (CatmullRom)\nwebp.Encode(quality=75)
IP --> H: {webpBytes, width, height}
H -> S3: Upload "chat/{convID}/{uuid}/conv.webp"
S3 --> H: OK
H -> S: SendMessage(…, attachmentKey, mime="image/webp")
S -> DB: INSERT chat_messages (attachment_*)
S -> Hub: SendToUser(B, {attachment_url})
Hub --> FB: 🖼 photo ready
H --> FA: 201 {attachment_url, attachment_mime:"image/webp"}

== Load history (keyset pagination) ==

A -> FA: scroll up
FA -> H: GET /conversations/{id}/messages\n?before=<RFC3339>&limit=50
H -> DB: SELECT … WHERE created_at < $before\nORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 50
note right: Index: (conversation_id, created_at DESC)\nO(log N) regardless of history size
DB --> H: messages → reverse → IsMine, attachment_url
H --> FA: 200 [{id, body, is_mine, created_at}]

== Mark as read ==

A -> FA: open conversation
FA -> H: POST /conversations/{id}/read
H -> DB: INSERT chat_reads ON CONFLICT DO UPDATE\nSET last_read_at = NOW()
H --> FA: 204

== Keepalive & slow-client drop ==

loop every 54s (pongWait × 9/10)
    Hub -> FB: conn.Ping(timeout=10s)
    FB --> Hub: Pong
end

Hub -> Hub: send buffer full (64 msgs)
Hub -> Hub: Unregister → close(client.send)
Hub -> FB: conn.CloseNow()

@enduml
